<!--
  Lyra appcast - host this file at:
  https://headroomstudio.dev/lyra/appcast.xml

  How to update for a new release:
  1. Run: make release  →  produces Lyra.dmg
  2. Upload Lyra.dmg to Cloudflare R2 as Lyra-X.Y.dmg, copy the public URL
  3. Get the file size in bytes:  wc -c < Lyra.dmg
  4. Sign the DMG with Sparkle:   .build/artifacts/sparkle/Sparkle/bin/sign_update Lyra.dmg
     (this prints the edSignature value)
  5. Add a new <item> block at the top (keep old items for reference)
  6. Push to your GitHub Pages repo - CloudFront picks it up automatically
-->
